Localization.Name: Testudo Backpack Deathblow
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Medium Backpack
Carrying Capacity: 105K µSCU
Core Compatibility: Medium & Heavy

Based on Quirinus Tech's Testudo medium backpack, the Deathblow variant has received unauthorized aftermarket modifications. The backpack may feel as light as a feather in your hands, but it can hold an impressive amount of weight thanks to its use of the same tough yet lightweight plating as the armor set.
